        </div>

      </div> <!-- demo container -->

      <h3>Why?</h3>
      Add a little flair to your system health dashboards.  Instead of numbers
      and graphs (yawn), you can instead use a fun visual indicator.

      <h3>Code</h3>
        <a href="https://github.com/ejfinneran/doomguy">github.com/ejfinneran/doomguy</a>


